{"tid":2493964,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"十大屋苑周末交投量繼續萎縮","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T17:17:48.000Z","uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de74187b52e314c18235a42b623ea7798afe51c5","tid":2493964,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"根據香港置業旗下分行截至今日下午3時統計，港、九及新界十大二手指標藍籌屋苑於本週末兩日合共錄10宗成交，與上周末的14宗成交比較，按週減少約29%，但仍保持連續9週雙位數水平，可見樓市承接力旺盛。本週末十大指標屋苑當中，有5個屋苑錄得成交，當中以沙田第一城錄得4宗最為活躍，其次為西九四小龍及美孚新邨，各錄得2宗；而太古城及將軍澳中心則各錄得1宗；其餘5個屋苑則未有錄得成交。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR7jnxi12oAeMZHGPwg6YzFmqAQ8fc4dHhqCxWR2sZoYh?filename=zAhLRQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAhLRQ1.jpg&h=6e5e5455&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c5d2a228fb1b7cd992cc7d59f4fba138205e4b4","tid":2493964,"uid":227441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"少得四宗就收皮啦on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ef07bbd3df19e7c02ac404e08eee40e5ccbbb9","tid":2493964,"uid":316048,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"無盤，你比幾多都無得買，業主開始SH<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe38cef082ffccc348a50c7c7a26b487350f566","tid":2493964,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0ef07bbd3df19e7c02ac404e08eee40e5ccbbb9","tid":2493964,"uid":316048,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"無盤，你比幾多都無得買，業主開始SH<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"如果真係業主封盤冇生意做，班AA就唔會起勢吹樓市GOGOGO ，等班業主心雄吊高嚟賣啦，根本個購買力正在萎縮中，面對現實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be42e2608a97530de0d824a2e33a90e979b0252","tid":2493964,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe38cef082ffccc348a50c7c7a26b487350f566","tid":2